commit.message: Updated SQL insertions and readme updates. Code cleanup in main.
Fixed RegEx to account for common name nomenclatures and typos. Cleanup of methods.
Program has been converted to running via command line with automated path variables and http requests. Example: >> python main.py grd20141EN.pdf
Modified CSV format, Database Helper file/function added to assist with organizing all data (experimental)
Actually fixed regex. Department total actually removed and extra newlines in professor names removed
Updated Main Py to loop over entire PDF to get all course contents and fixed various issues with empty pages/no courses
Updated Regex to account for empty PDF pages or pages without courses on them. Writing all data to CSV file for database testing
Regex for prof, GPA, grades, and course separated out into lists, ready for processing
PDF parser updated with Regex to extract courses and grades (course total being included incorrectly)
